Your empathic nature shows itself during this period of your life. You will develop a sense of connectedness with the people around you and even with those whom you have never met. You will find yourself rejoicing, anguishing, celebrating and crying through many experiences that don't impact you directly. You will learn to champion tolerance and love as your most valued ideals. You will likely be drawn to humanitarian causes and feel the need to “fix” things in people and in society. Be careful to tread where your help is wanted. Do not force your love, benevolence, philanthropy or charity on people. The right people and situations will find their way to you and you will recognize them when you encounter them.
